quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,35,"Keefeero on naati ka ngesa makko himo wonndi e gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 on fii yo o hollu mo mba, tawi himo tooﾃｱiri hoore-makko keeferaaku e hawtaare, keefeero on wi'i: "Mi sikkaa mbaa ngasa mba sutiﾉ預a+ndaarataa ﾉ熔o lannay; sabu ko mi waﾉ預ni mba kon e sababuuji heddagol"."
  18,36,"Mi sikkaa Darngal ngal waﾉ預y, pellet, ﾉ預'an ko ngurndan duumiiﾉ預n, si tawii le ngal daroyi si mi immintinaama mi artiraama ka Joomi an, mi heﾉ殿y ﾉ殿awo immital ngal ko mi ruttoo e mun, huunde ﾉ砥runde mbaa ngesa an. Wonugol an galo ka aduna ﾉ熔o ﾉ蓉n no holli nde mi wonoyta galo ﾉ殿awo immital ngal."
  18,37,"Wonndiiﾉ熔 makko gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 on tawi himo ruttannde mo haala kan o wi'i mo: "Enee a yeddii On Taguﾉ熔 baaba maaﾉ預 Aadama e mbullaari, refti O Tagumaa an e maniiyu, refti O waﾉ蓉maa neﾉ遼預nke gorko, O fonni tere maaﾉ容n O waﾉ蓉maa timmuﾉ熔, awa On Hattanﾉ熔 e dow ﾉ擁iﾉ熔o fow ko O Hattanﾉ熔 immintinngol ma"."
  18,38,"Kono min mi wi'ataa ngool kongol maa ﾉ熔o, anndu ko mi wi'ata: Kanko Alla Senayee wonanii Mo Joomi an ﾆ「rnirﾉ熔 Neemaaji Makko ﾉ擁n e amen, mi kafidataa=renndintaa Mo hay e gooto ka Dewal."
  18,39,"Hanno tuma nde naatuﾉ預a ka ngesa maaﾉ預 wi'aa: "Ko Alla muuyi kon doole alanaa hay gooto si wanna Alla, ko Kanko woni waﾉ熔owo ko O faalaa ko Kanko woni Dolnuﾉ熔, si a wonii ndaara miﾉ熔 ﾉ砥rumaa ﾉ妬llaade e fanﾉ蓉de ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎."
  18,40,"Min miﾉ熔 tijjii nde Alla okkinmi moﾆｴﾆｴore ﾉ砥rnde ngesa maa mban, e nde O nulata e ngesa maa mban lepte immorde ka kammu, ngesa maaﾉ預 mban wonta leydi ndi puﾉ擁 alaa e mun hara teppe mortoto e mayri sabu ﾉ登wrugol mayri."
  18,41,"Maaﾉ蓉n ndiyan mabba ﾉ預n ila muta ka nder leydi, hara a hattantaake yottorgol e majjan wallitorkun, si ndiyan mabba ﾉ預n mutii hara heddagol alanaa ﾉ預n."
  18,42,"Ko gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 on tijjinoo kon halkuyee=halkaare huuﾉ妬ti dimﾉ容 ngesa keefeero on,keefeero on wattini himo waylita newe makko ﾉ容n ka sattude suno e nimse e dow ko o rokki kon jawle fii dankagol mba e moﾆｴﾆｴinngol mba, ngesa mban ko yanumba e hoore tugaale mun, ﾉ容n ﾉ容 calﾉ擁 inabuuje ﾉ容n layi hoore mun,himo wi'a: "Ee jalla wonno min,mi gomﾉ擁nno Joomi an Kanko Tun, hara mi kafidaano e Makko hay e gooto e jeyaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  18,43,"Laatanaaki oo keefeero jamaa wallooﾉ兎 mo immorde e lepte jippiiﾉ容 e makko ﾉ容n, ko kanko non wonnoo wasorde jamaa, kanko o laataaki sakkotooﾉ熔 Alla e halkugol ngesa mban."
  18,44,"No e nder nden darorde Ballal Alla ngal Kanko tun, ko Kanko Seniiﾉ熔 On woni Moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ熔 mbarjaari wonannde yiﾉ遼兎 Makko gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ko Kanko sowanta ﾉ兎 mbarjaari ndin, e Moﾆｴﾆｴo battane wonannde ﾉ兎."
  18,45,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, piyan ﾉ兎n hoditorﾉ兎 aduna misal, yeru ngurndan aduna e nattingol mun e yaawude lannude mun ko yeru ndiyan toﾉ登, ﾉ預n Men jippini ﾉ蓉n immorde ka kammu, fuﾉ擁ri sabu ﾉ預n ndiyan puﾉ擁 leydi ndin ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎nndi, ﾉ擁n puﾉ擁 wonti heluﾉ擁 muncii, keneeli ﾉ擁n no ronndoo kuntoy majji naﾉ妬ra e banﾅ菊eji goo, leydi ndin ruttoo no ndi wonirnoo, Alla yenﾉ擁i ko O Hattanﾉ熔 e dow kala huunde, huunde ronkintaa Mo, hiMo wurna ko O yiﾉ擁, O re'a ko O yiﾉ擁."